## Resources & References

The following resources were used during the development of this project:

Angular Testing Guide
 – For understanding and writing unit tests.

Angular Routing Overview
 – For route management.

Angular Signals Guide
 – For implementing reactive state management with signals.

Angular Material Dialog Styling
 – For customizing modal dialogs.

StackOverflow: No provider for ActivatedRoute
 – For resolving routing-related testing issues.

